image_analysis.description: A photograph of an interior staircase. The stairs are covered in a dark grey patterned carpet. To the left is a blue metal railing with a wooden handrail. The walls are painted a light beige or off-white color. A circular flush-mount light fixture is illuminated on the ceiling at the top of the stairs. There is an electrical outlet visible on the wall at the landing level. The image appears to be taken from a lower step looking up.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical composition showing a staircase leading to a landing.
